fly/advanced-tuning"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to dynamically adjust your alpha parameter over time to improve convergence in highly complex multidimensional spaces. "},{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"\alpha"}},{"type":"text","text":" + 2"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}
